---------------------
Rasta, The Rst Editor
---------------------

Live view supported Qt4 based Webkit integrated Rst editor for Pardus Developers and all others.

Requirements:
=============

* python
* qt4
* PyQt
* docutils
* qscintilla2
* qscintilla2-python

How to Run:
===========
::

Install all the required packages

$ python setup.py build
$ ./rasta

For Developers:
===============
After modifying the ui file you need to update pythonic ui file too::

    $ pyuic4 gui/mainWindow.ui -o rastaLib/mainWindow.py

And for icon changes you must update the rc file::

    $ pyrcc4 core/icons.qrc -o rastaLib/icons_rc.py

Have fun.
